web_snippets: Abel Makkonen Tesfaye (Amharic: አቤል መኮንን ተስፋዬ; né Abel Tesfaye, born February 16, 1990), known professionally as the Weeknd, is a Canadian singer-songwriter, ...
Abel Tesfaye, better known as The Weeknd, is a Grammy-winning R&B singer responsible for such hits as “Can't Feel My Face,” “The Hills,”and “Blinding Lights.”
